			<name>
				<baseName xml:lang="en">Softener</baseName>
				<baseName xml:lang="zh">柔软剂</baseName>
			</name>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">Water softener; Magnetic water softener</common:synonyms>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="zh">Water softener; Magnetic water softener</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification>
					<common:category level="0">Materials production</common:category>
					<common:category level="1">Other materials</common:category>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">A softener is a device that eliminates hard water without losing health benefits, maintaining some levels of calcium and magnesium. This salt-free softener is ideal for those with high-sodium diets who need to eliminate hard water but don't want to reduce mineral intake. Water softeners work by removing hard water minerals and replacing them with sodium and potassium in a process referred to as ion exchange. They remove heavy minerals like calcium, iron, and magnesium from the water supply as it enters the home.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">软水器是一种既能消除硬水，又能保持一定水平的钙和镁，同时又不失健康益处的设备。这种无盐软水器非常适合那些需要去除硬水但又不想减少矿物质摄入量的高钠饮食者。软水器的工作原理是去除硬水中的矿物质，并在称为离子交换的过程中用钠和钾取代它们。软水器能在水进入家庭时去除自来水中的钙、铁和镁等重矿物质。</common:generalComment>
